 302:   interact within the exploratory apparatus). Separately, a later
 303:   pre-registered symmetric gate — a **selection-only** test with delivery held
 304:   at parity — finds the *selection* advantage positive but small (Section 6);
 305:   it does not test the delivery interaction. This work also introduces the
 306:   visibility gap (officially reported minus real delivery) as a
 307:   measurable accountability deficit of the status quo;
 308: 
