 746: salience destination preserves late-cycle alignment slightly better —
 747: plausibly because amplified social proof also propagates evaluator
 748: seeding). What governs robustness to decay is the structural share of the
 749: default layer itself, Finding 2's variable. Engagement decay — the
 750: documented fate of civic-tech participation (Hirschman 1970; Peixoto and
 751: Fox 2016) — is a
 752: buffered risk here, but the buffer is the institutional layer's size, and
